@node "nws1" "WOA98"

@{fg shine} World Of Amiga 1998@{fg text}

 The World Of Amiga show is back for 1998, it will be held on the
16th - 17th of May in the Novotel, London, ENGLAND. There is already
and impressive list of companys signed up to be at the show with
many more signing up all the time. Some of the exhibitors will be
Amiga International, Power Computing, CU Amiga, Amiga Format, Epic
Marketing, Blittersoft, Weird Science and many more. There will
be a wide screen TV room which will be showing the FA Cup final
live and also talked about is a huge networked game of Quake. 
Tickets prices will be as follows : Adults, £7.50 and Children,
£5.50, call the ticket hotline on @{b}(+44) 01369 708029@{ub} or email
enquirys for trade or stand infos should be sent to :
@{b}woa@cu-amiga.co.uk@{ub}

