These prices are valid for pre\box systems in an ATX minitower, including
mouse and keyboard, as well as AMIGA OS 3.1 and the PowerUP System
Software, excluding memory, harddrive and CD-ROM. For an entry-level
configuration of memory, harddrive and CD-ROM (32MB, 4GB, 24speed) an
